    "description": "A Social Sim + Turn-Based RPG with a 3rd grade protagonist! 📆PLAN your days, 🧑‍🤝‍🧑BEFRIEND characters, 🧱COLLECT+CRAFT unique attacks, and ⚔️FIGHT in Turn-based combat with Action Commands!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                         Face Your Nightmares!                                     </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/ca2c135a69e2256428a77b09c6f63baa.poster.avif?t=1719953078\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/ca2c135a69e2256428a77b09c6f63baa.webm?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/ca2c135a69e2256428a77b09c6f63baa.mp4?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- Weird recurring nightmares are showing up all over!<br>- Solve the mystery of who or what is causing chaos!<br>- Each nightmare has different enemies representing the dreamer's darkest fears. <br>- Defeat them in Turn-Based Combat with Action Commands!<br>- Time your attacks well enough, and deal bonus damage!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Collect Toys, Create Skills! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/9fbd04dd4a9cf803cebba289145ecd58.poster.avif?t=1719953078\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/9fbd04dd4a9cf803cebba289145ecd58.webm?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/9fbd04dd4a9cf803cebba289145ecd58.mp4?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take your toys to use as weapons in the dream world!<br>- Find, earn, and trade different toys to get stronger!<br>- Craft your own Plastik Sword with unique skills to use in battle. <br>- Do you want an attack that's cheap and reliable? Or how about that will end quickly end a battle? It's your choice!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Hang out with friends! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/f145e263891fce61373933b840240e9c.poster.avif?t=1719953078\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/f145e263891fce61373933b840240e9c.webm?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/f145e263891fce61373933b840240e9c.mp4?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Overcome your shyness and make friends with your classmates, parents, or unlikely strangers!<br>- Play in all kinds of different places and in different ways!<br>- Each of your friends give you different rewards<br>- Create different combat builds based on their rewards!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Play your days carefully! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/9821db6048709a21287a986952d6f155.poster.avif?t=1719953078\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/9821db6048709a21287a986952d6f155.webm?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780130/extras/9821db6048709a21287a986952d6f155.mp4?t=1719953078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- You only have a limited number of days to meet your deadlines. <br>- While hanging out with friends will help, there are imminent threats to face that won't wait for you.",
